    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a mechanically sound driver\u2019s example, featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine with its signature individual throttle bodies and an 8,000 RPM redline. Power is managed through a Getrag six-speed manual transmission and delivered to the pavement via a torque-sensing limited-slip differential. The chassis has been enhanced with a reinforced rear subframe to address known floor fatigue, and the suspension geometry remains true with refreshed control arm bushings. The VANOS unit has been meticulously serviced to ensure precise variable valve timing across the power band. While the finish shows minor road-going patina, the performance envelope remains sharp, offering the tactile steering feedback and balanced weight distribution this chassis is renowned for.",
