      "description": "Presenting a meticulously maintained luxury SUV that perfectly balances rugged capability with refined comfort. This vehicle has been a reliable companion, primarily used for family road trips and highway commuting. The exterior shines in its original factory paint, though close inspection reveals a few minor stone chips on the hood and a small scuff on the rear bumper\u2014typical for a vehicle of this age that has been enjoyed on the open road. Inside, the premium leather seating remains supple and free of tears, though the driver\u2019s seat shows light bolster wear consistent with regular use. All cabin electronics, including the touchscreen navigation, multi-zone climate control, and premium surround-sound system, function flawlessly. Mechanically, this car is in excellent health; it comes with a comprehensive service history, including a recent professional inspection, oil change, and brake service. It sits on a set of high-quality tires with plenty of tread remaining. It starts up instantly, shifts smoothly through all gears, and offers a quiet, composed ride. This is an ideal choice for a buyer seeking a dependable, turn-key vehicle that has been treated with care.",
